If we're concerned about the 2500 tx thing, we could limit that here couldn't we? ie:

```c++
int low_fee_removed = 0;
while (!empty() && low_fee_removed < 100) {
    ...
    if (removed < m_min_relay_feerate && DynamicMemoryUsage() <= sizelimit) {
        ++low_fee_removed;
    }
    ...
}
```

